沁园春·天象
Ode to the Celestial Order

北宇茫茫，  
光影循环，  
寰宇无疆。  
—The northern heavens vast and boundless,  
light and shadow turning without end,  
the cosmos without border or wall.

看恒星闪烁，似真似幻；  
银河翻涌，如梦如光。  
—Behold the stars, flickering—half truth, half illusion;  
the Milky Way surges, like dream made radiant.

量子浮沉，时间互换，  
力与能交映成章。  
—Quanta rise and fall, time and space exchange;  
force and energy weave themselves into law.

叹世道——  
昔日王侯霸业，  
皆尘皆凉。  
—Ah, the fate of ages!  
Kings and conquerors of old—  
all dust, all cold remains.

今朝数理如浪，  
可推天机，亦解地方。  
—Yet now the tides of number surge anew,  
revealing heaven’s code, deciphering the earth.

借开普之律，洞察运行；  
引爱因之智，照亮时光。  
—Through Kepler’s law we trace the unseen orbits;  
through Einstein’s light, we illuminate time.

价有定频，周期有序，  
自然不语自成纲。  
—Price flows by resonance, cycle by rhythm;  
Nature speaks without words, yet coherence prevails.

数天选人物，还看今早！  
—Count the Heaven-Chosen minds—  
the destined thinkers of this dawn!

此词不叹山河人物，而叙宇宙法则。

作者以科学为诗，以时间与价格、能量与秩序为语言，将牛顿、开普勒与爱因斯坦之理融汇人类精神的觉醒。

“数天选人物，还看今早”，象征新时代“天命与智识”的合一。

